Indeed. Nandinho is the one.
who's dying to see "Jaws".

751
01:09:17.195 --> 01:09:19.782
I was thinking of bringing him
with me Saturday morning.

752
01:09:19.823 --> 01:09:21.533
You're crazy. Mr. Alexandre.

753
01:09:22.784 --> 01:09:24.411
I'd let him see it.
if it was up to me.

754
01:09:24.453 --> 01:09:26.454
No. the film is too intense for him.

755
01:09:27.164 --> 01:09:30.834
The kid has nightmares.
just from seeing the poster.

756
01:10:10.502 --> 01:10:11.669
There's something going on.

757
01:10:12.045 --> 01:10:14.381
This happens every single day.

758
01:10:14.423 --> 01:10:15.924
Every single day.

759
01:10:34.778 --> 01:10:37.113
Fátima used to love that window.

760
01:10:38.407 --> 01:10:40.908
She liked to sit right there.
where you are.

761
01:10:44.288 --> 01:10:46.248
I want to ask you a question.

762
01:10:46.665 --> 01:10:48.042
Looking in the eye.

763
01:10:59.846 --> 01:11:01.848
When you two were married.

764
01:11:03.641 --> 01:11:05.852
you fucked around a lot. didn't you?

765
01:11:06.436 --> 01:11:09.439
What are you on about.
after all this time?

766
01:11:11.525 --> 01:11:13.235
Did you. or didn't you?

767
01:11:16.113 --> 01:11:17.490
Mr. Alexandre...

768
01:11:19.367 --> 01:11:22.119
Fátima and I loved each other
very much.

769
01:11:23.746 --> 01:11:26.832
And you know that better than anyone.
don't you?

770
01:11:26.874 --> 01:11:27.708
I do.

771
01:11:28.210 --> 01:11:30.294
Fernando is the greatest proof of that.

772
01:11:30.796 --> 01:11:31.922
Now.

773
01:11:32.254 --> 01:11:34.466
did you or did you not fuck around?

774
01:11:43.651 --> 01:11:45.520
Hello? Just a minute.

775
01:11:45.561 --> 01:11:46.396
Phone call.

776
01:11:47.280 --> 01:11:51.109
Hello! Hey João. it worked. right?

777
01:11:51.484 --> 01:11:54.444
It's good to talk to you. It's good
to know you're doing well. you know?

778
01:11:54.575 --> 01:11:57.596
I must be quick.
I don't have many tokens.

779
01:11:57.696 --> 01:11:58.899
Let me tell you.

780
01:11:59.534 --> 01:12:03.122
<i>He managed to get your name
on the Federal Police's list.</i>

781
01:12:03.162 --> 01:12:06.082
<i>That means you can't leave the country.</i>

782
01:12:06.124 --> 01:12:07.292
<i>That's very bizarre.</i>

783
01:12:07.334 --> 01:12:09.043
I can't travel?

784
01:12:09.420 --> 01:12:11.255
I'm trying to understand.

785
01:12:11.547 --> 01:12:13.632
He's pulling his strings.

786
01:12:13.674 --> 01:12:16.594
That's playing dirty.
at the highest level.

787
01:12:16.636 --> 01:12:18.304
I'm telling you.

788
01:12:18.846 --> 01:12:21.975
he managed to get
a serious prosecutor off the case.

789
01:12:22.016 --> 01:12:23.642
pro-regime. but serious...

790
01:12:23.684 --> 01:12:25.477
and had him replaced by a crook.

791
01:12:25.519 --> 01:12:26.896
<i>a friend of his from Rio.</i>

792
01:12:26.938 --> 01:12:28.189
What the fuck is this João?

793
01:12:28.606 --> 01:12:30.316
I have to say.

794
01:12:30.692 --> 01:12:32.987
I don't like this at all.

795
01:12:33.029 --> 01:12:34.404
So please.

796
01:12:34.446 --> 01:12:37.908
<i>don't expose yourself.
stay in the shadows.</i>

797
01:12:37.950 --> 01:12:39.744
</i>- Okay. this is my last token.</i>-
- OK.

798
01:12:40.536 --> 01:12:41.829
Listen carefully.

799
01:12:42.788 --> 01:12:44.081
Elza.

800
01:12:44.123 --> 01:12:47.084
is the name of the most important
character in this story. now.

801
01:12:47.753 --> 01:12:49.128
Elza.

802
01:13:37.930 --> 01:13:39.306
Great place. isn’t it?

803
01:13:39.723 --> 01:13:41.726
The Rio technician stays here.
you know?

804
01:13:41.768 --> 01:13:43.645
The company saves on hotel expenses.

805
01:13:52.904 --> 01:13:53.905
Mr. Alexandre?

806
01:13:54.405 --> 01:13:56.534
Alexandre de Jesus do Nascimento.
at your service.

807
01:13:56.575 --> 01:13:58.369
- I'm Elza.
- Pleased to meet you.

808
01:13:59.120 --> 01:14:00.413
- I'm Valdemar.
- Hello.

809
01:14:01.872 --> 01:14:03.581
What should I call you?

810
01:14:03.623 --> 01:14:06.127
Here. you can call me
by my name. Armando.

811
01:14:07.962 --> 01:14:10.506
Such an honor to talk to you here.

812
01:14:10.548 --> 01:14:12.884
You didn't say you were using
a fake name.

813
01:14:12.926 --> 01:14:14.928
It's not badly done. is it?

814
01:14:17.848 --> 01:14:20.141
Yes. it's kind of poorly done.

815
01:14:20.933 --> 01:14:24.730
And thanks for the free tickets.
We just saw the movie.

816
01:14:25.188 --> 01:14:26.314
Did you like it?

817
01:14:26.773 --> 01:14:30.278
I'm not a religious person.
but it was scary.

818
01:14:30.736 --> 01:14:32.863
Valdemar almost shit himself.

819
01:14:32.904 --> 01:14:34.614
I don't like horror movies.

820
01:14:41.372 --> 01:14:42.915
Can I record our conversation?

821
01:14:43.374 --> 01:14:44.960
Record whatever your like.

822
01:14:50.339 --> 01:14:51.592
Recording.

823
01:14:52.259 --> 01:14:53.885
This is like...

824
01:14:55.679 --> 01:15:00.309
those American
witness protection programs.

825
01:15:03.729 --> 01:15:07.150
There... everything is done
with a lot of money 

826
01:15:07.192 --> 01:15:09.485
and by their government. right...

827
01:15:09.526 --> 01:15:13.782
Over here. it's all a bit
improvised. Brazilian style.

828
01:15:13.823 --> 01:15:16.326
And to protect you from Brazil.

829
01:15:17.535 --> 01:15:19.747
How many people are you helping?

830
01:15:20.205 --> 01:15:23.166
Including you.
four people here in Recife.

831
01:15:23.834 --> 01:15:26.920
Plus. two in Fortaleza
and one in Salvador.

832
01:15:27.821 --> 01:15:30.716
And are all the people from Recife
in the same building as me?

833
01:15:33.886 --> 01:15:36.515
Look. each case is different.

834
01:15:36.555 --> 01:15:39.767
- So. we all help each other.
- Right.

835
01:15:41.602 --> 01:15:43.855
And who's paying for all this?

836
01:15:46.233 --> 01:15:48.360
It's paid for by the daughter...

837
01:15:49.112 --> 01:15:52.155
of a very wealthy São Paulo family.

838
01:15:53.073 --> 01:15:55.493
that has been robbing the country
for a long time.

839
01:15:58.746 --> 01:16:00.914
How was it at work today?

840
01:16:02.041 --> 01:16:06.170
So. you placed me
at a police station. seriously?

841
01:16:06.212 --> 01:16:08.214
No! No. it's not a police station.

842
01:16:08.256 --> 01:16:11.301
You asked for the
Institute for Identification.

843
01:16:11.343 --> 01:16:12.177
I did.

844
01:16:12.510 --> 01:16:14.470
I'll try to find

845
01:16:14.512 --> 01:16:16.932
the only document that proves

846
01:16:17.641 --> 01:16:20.477
that my late mother did exist.

847
01:16:22.020 --> 01:16:24.648
But now.
that place is a police station.

848
01:16:24.690 --> 01:16:26.024
There is a Police Chief there.

849
01:16:26.400 --> 01:16:27.777
Did you two talk?

850
01:16:29.779 --> 01:16:34.284
That guy's a jerk. isn't he?
A real son of a bitch.

851
01:16:34.825 --> 01:16:36.327
The worst thing is that...

852
01:16:37.829 --> 01:16:39.789
he seemed to like me.

853
01:16:40.248 --> 01:16:43.210
Just so you know.
we have an ally there.

854
01:16:43.626 --> 01:16:44.794
Anísio.

855
01:16:47.298 --> 01:16:49.382
Is it OK for him to know who I am?

856
01:16:50.009 --> 01:16:51.342
Anísio is helping.

857
01:16:51.761 --> 01:16:54.597
But he doesn't know who you are.
or what's being done to you.

858
01:16:56.016 --> 01:16:57.934
How's the passport situation going?

859
01:16:58.476 --> 01:17:00.394
Mine and my son's?

860
01:17:00.978 --> 01:17:03.898
Don't know if you're aware.
but I'm on a list.

861
01:17:05.150 --> 01:17:08.987
of the Federal Police
banning me from travelling.

862
01:17:09.529 --> 01:17:11.531
Given the situation.

863
01:17:11.574 --> 01:17:15.827
we agree that you need a fake passport.

864
01:17:16.703 --> 01:17:18.705
We can handle that.

865
01:17:18.747 --> 01:17:22.710
I can get you those documents.
but it'll take a few days.

866
01:17:22.752 --> 01:17:25.171
Elza. what's going on?
I don't understand.

867
01:17:25.212 --> 01:17:27.757
Why do I need a fake passport?

868
01:17:28.883 --> 01:17:30.803
I've done nothing wrong...

869
01:17:32.345 --> 01:17:33.971
And what's in it for you?

870
01:17:34.305 --> 01:17:35.641
Who are you?

871
01:17:35.682 --> 01:17:37.643
I'm a pediatrician.

872
01:17:37.684 --> 01:17:39.520
I'm only trying to help.

873
01:17:39.561 --> 01:17:41.939
Armando. it's not about that now.

874
01:17:42.481 --> 01:17:44.650
Think about your son. of my grandson.

875
01:17:45.734 --> 01:17:47.694
Think about my daughter. Fátima.

876
01:17:48.195 --> 01:17:51.908
Mr. Alexandre.
all I do is thinking about my son.

877
01:17:52.992 --> 01:17:55.829
I'm very sorry about your daughter.
Mr. Alexandre.

878
01:17:56.245 --> 01:17:58.331
And your wife. Armando.

879
01:18:00.875 --> 01:18:04.129
How could this country
lose someone like Fátima?

880
01:18:06.297 --> 01:18:08.634
Brazil will pay dearly for that.

881
01:18:09.175 --> 01:18:11.010
I disagree.

882
01:18:11.052 --> 01:18:12.804
With all due respect. you know.

883
01:18:13.763 --> 01:18:15.474
It'll pay nothing.

884
01:18:15.975 --> 01:18:17.852
It won't pay shit.

885
01:18:19.396 --> 01:18:21.440
Armando. I admire you.

886
01:18:21.480 --> 01:18:23.400
but you should leave!

887
01:18:24.400 --> 01:18:27.028
If I was you.
I'd get the hell out of here!

888
01:18:27.070 --> 01:18:29.447
I'd take their help and leave today!

889
01:18:29.489 --> 01:18:31.158
That's why I've arranged all this!

890
01:18:32.199 --> 01:18:33.535
Mr. Alexandre...

891
01:18:33.577 --> 01:18:36.121
We need to protect what we still have.

892
01:18:36.163 --> 01:18:37.998
You and my grandson.

893
01:18:47.758 --> 01:18:50.845
I'll be in the projection booth.
Lock from the inside.

894
01:18:57.560 --> 01:18:59.562
We would like to know more

895
01:18:59.604 --> 01:19:02.149
about Henrique Castro Ghirotti.

896
01:19:02.191 --> 01:19:04.275
and how he got involved in this.

897
01:19:06.445 --> 01:19:08.072
I'll let it all out.

898
01:19:08.113 --> 01:19:09.406
I'll get this

899
01:19:10.157 --> 01:19:11.659
off my chest.

900
01:19:12.242 --> 01:19:13.745
It's a conversation.

901
01:19:14.621 --> 01:19:15.913
Recorded.

902
01:19:17.123 --> 01:19:18.500
Tell me about this...

903
01:19:20.168 --> 01:19:21.836
Henrique Ghirotti.

904
01:19:46.571 --> 01:19:47.656
I...

905
01:19:48.781 --> 01:19:51.451
am not a violent person.

906
01:19:55.997 --> 01:19:57.582
But this man...

907
01:20:02.421 --> 01:20:04.673
I'd kill him with a hammer.

908
01:20:13.099 --> 01:20:15.977
I'd bash his head completely
with a hammer.

909
01:20:16.812 --> 01:20:17.646
Do you...

910
01:20:19.021 --> 01:20:20.482
carry a gun?

911
01:20:24.945 --> 01:20:27.072
No. but I know how to use a hammer.

912
01:20:29.408 --> 01:20:31.076
I need to go to the bathroom.

913
01:20:35.664 --> 01:20:37.624
I need to go to the bathroom.

914
01:20:40.003 --> 01:20:42.171
She paused recording to go pee...

915
01:20:48.136 --> 01:20:50.263
<i>We'd like to know more</i>

916
01:20:50.305 --> 01:20:52.348
<i>about Henrique Castro Ghirotti.</i>

917
01:20:52.390 --> 01:20:54.518
<i>and how he got involved in this case.</i>

918
01:20:54.560 --> 01:20:55.469
Flávia?

919
01:20:56.228 --> 01:20:57.146
Flávia?

920
01:20:57.563 --> 01:20:59.190
...off my chest.
Flávia?

921
01:20:59.231 --> 01:21:00.524
It's a conversation.

922
01:21:00.565 --> 01:21:02.526
Which date are you listening to?

923
01:21:03.277 --> 01:21:06.323
- Sorry?
- Which date are you listening to?

924
01:21:06.989 --> 01:21:09.492
It's Elza with "Marcelo". in quotes.

925
01:21:09.533 --> 01:21:11.870
February 25. 1977.

926
01:21:11.912 --> 01:21:13.872
I haven't finished it yet. though.

927
01:21:14.246 --> 01:21:16.666
Marcelo is Armando.
you know that. right?

928
01:21:18.001 --> 01:21:20.253
Ah... That's what I just heard here.

929
01:21:20.295 --> 01:21:22.005
but I got confused.

930
01:21:22.047 --> 01:21:24.675
So. Marcelo is actually Armando.

931
01:21:25.175 --> 01:21:27.678
- It's a fake name.
- Exactly.

932
01:21:27.719 --> 01:21:29.763
You're clever. Flávia!

933
01:21:29.805 --> 01:21:31.349
Which one are you listening to?

934
01:21:31.765 --> 01:21:33.893
The tape of Anísio.

935
01:21:33.935 --> 01:21:35.645
Of '76.

936
01:21:35.686 --> 01:21:36.604
I understood.

937
01:21:42.693 --> 01:21:44.487
<i>I need to go to the bathroom.</i>

938
01:21:51.161 --> 01:21:53.247
How did you meet Ghirotti?

939
01:21:54.749 --> 01:21:58.001
He came on a visit to the university.

940
01:21:58.836 --> 01:22:01.839
As head of department.

941
01:22:02.215 --> 01:22:06.386
I'd sometimes meet guests
at the airport. here in Recife.

942
01:22:06.428 --> 01:22:09.806
He was on the board
of directors of Eletrobras.

943
01:22:09.848 --> 01:22:12.350
under the Ministry of Mines and Energy.

944
01:22:12.392 --> 01:22:13.727
So. you're Armando.

945
01:22:14.686 --> 01:22:16.479
I read your CV.

946
01:22:16.521 --> 01:22:18.858
I thought you were
a different kind of person.

947
01:22:19.274 --> 01:22:22.236
- I'll take it as a compliment.
- Yes. Hot. isn't it?

948
01:22:22.278 --> 01:22:24.155
So. what was your first impression?

949
01:22:24.447 --> 01:22:25.531
Of Ghirotti?

950
01:22:25.573 --> 01:22:26.657
A piece of shit.

951
01:22:28.200 --> 01:22:29.994
And his son. another piece of shit.

952
01:22:31.496 --> 01:22:33.956
How long have you been
head of department?

953
