1020
01:25:45.910 --> 01:25:49.080
Unless you haven't read it.

1021
01:25:49.122 --> 01:25:51.707
Let me finish.
I also spoke in a positive way.

1022
01:25:51.749 --> 01:25:54.169
- Just to get that clear.
- It's a compliment.

1023
01:25:54.502 --> 01:25:55.838
Ah. all right...

1024
01:25:56.296 --> 01:25:59.340
Including this leather tanning
technology.

1025
01:26:00.008 --> 01:26:02.719
the one measures the surface area
of the leather.

1026
01:26:03.512 --> 01:26:06.306
I think is important
for the local culture.

1027
01:26:07.182 --> 01:26:09.101
The ox. the goat. the cow.

1028
01:26:09.769 --> 01:26:12.605
are relevant for the economy
of the Northeast Region.

1029
01:26:12.647 --> 01:26:13.897
I like it.

1030
01:26:15.733 --> 01:26:19.404
This is a regional center.
it's not a national center.

1031
01:26:19.446 --> 01:26:21.322
much less an international one.

1032
01:26:22.907 --> 01:26:26.536
The electric car. for example.
a project that you presented to me.

1033
01:26:26.578 --> 01:26:28.914
By the way.
Armando is also working on it.

1034
01:26:30.498 --> 01:26:33.043
