1038
01:26:42.596 --> 01:26:46.475
You and your company
are part of that project.

1039
01:26:46.516 --> 01:26:47.975
Eletrobras.

1040
01:26:48.018 --> 01:26:52.355
Eletrobras has indeed acquired
12 prototypes from the consortium.

1041
01:26:52.939 --> 01:26:54.300
Eletrobras?

1042
01:26:54.399 --> 01:26:57.027
- Not your own company?
- Eletrobras. May I carry on?

1043
01:26:59.696 --> 01:27:00.614
So...

1044
01:27:00.655 --> 01:27:02.909
