from abroad.

1052
01:27:22.596 --> 01:27:23.680
Dr. Ghirotti.

1053
01:27:24.306 --> 01:27:27.351
I'm Luanda Azevedo.
I'm a research professor.

1054
01:27:27.392 --> 01:27:30.438
with a degree from the Federal
University of Rio Grande do Sul.

1055
01:27:30.480 --> 01:27:32.731
- You are a gaúcha?
- Yes. I am from the South.

1056
01:27:33.108 --> 01:27:35.735
All our projects are funded

1057
01:27:35.777 --> 01:27:38.655
