trust money.

1060
01:27:44.536 --> 01:27:47.581
It's time to rethink
your funding criteria.

1061
01:27:47.623 --> 01:27:49.834
and most importantly. independence.
right?

1062
01:27:50.876 --> 01:27:53.671
<i>Luanda. in fact.
was our first casualty.</i>

1063
01:27:53.712 --> 01:27:55.214
<i>She went to work</i>

1064
01:27:55.673 --> 01:27:57.633
