1066
01:28:03.432 --> 01:28:05.183
And did this happen to the whole team?

1067
01:28:06.393 --> 01:28:07.393
It did.

1068
01:28:07.685 --> 01:28:10.230
It was a real "industry makeover".

1069
01:28:11.313 --> 01:28:15.111
<i>He dried up public university funding.</i</i>

1070
01:28:15.152 --> 01:28:16.946
<i>of a public university.
for personal benefit.</i</i>

1071
01:28:17.279 --> 01:28:18.739
