1096
01:30:36.260 --> 01:30:38.304
It's a simple advancement. 
it's a simple patent.

1097
01:30:38.373 --> 01:30:39.740
But it's mine. Henrique.

1098
01:30:41.425 --> 01:30:42.587
Give me a whiskey. please.

1099
