This is a man.

1152
01:33:37.389 --> 01:33:38.391
Let's go.

1153
01:33:38.642 --> 01:33:40.790
You're drunk. You're drunk.

1154
01:33:41.480 --> 01:33:43.768
This is a disgrace.
